# ║  BUG REGISTRY v3.30.24.6  (fixes applied over v3.30.24.5)              ║
# ║                                                                          ║
# ║  BUG-JSON-001 [FIXED]  Per-image JSON missing extraction values          ║
# ║    process_batch, _run_fix_auto, _run_fix_manual wrote minimal JSON     ║
# ║    (temperature_celsius only). No YOLO box, spot_box, raw DN, or        ║
# ║    Planck/atmosphere params were stored.                                 ║
# ║    Fix: each spot now includes an "extraction" block (yolo_box,         ║
# ║    spot_box, hotspot_pixel, raw_dn_at_hotspot, region_raw_dn_min/max,   ║
# ║    yolo_confidence). Top-level "extraction_metadata" stores Planck       ║
# ║    constants, atmosphere params, unit, spot_box_size, model_path, and   ║
