# ║                                                                          ║
# ║  Detection logic (priority order):                                       ║
# ║    1. FLIR_RUNTIME env-var  → explicit override                         ║
# ║    2. fastapi/uvicorn in sys.modules → running inside web server        ║
# ║    3. Linux + no DISPLAY → headless server                              ║
# ║    4. tkinter display probe → local desktop                             ║
# ║    5. Fallback → "local" (safe default for direct script execution)     ║
