# JOBS_BASE_DIR: root under which per-job isolated working directories live.
#   Override via FLIR_JOBS_DIR environment variable.
#   Each job creates: <JOBS_BASE_DIR>/<job_id>/  with input copies + outputs.
# UPLOAD_BASE_DIR: where user-uploaded image folders are placed temporarily.
# MAX_UPLOAD_FOLDER_MB: soft cap on total size of a single batch folder (MB).
# MIN_FREE_DISK_MB: abort batch if free disk < this value before starting.
# MAX_ACTIVE_JOBS_PER_USER: throttle concurrent jobs per session token.
# ============================================================================
