            # occupies <~14% of the SpotBoxSize box as a glint and masks it entirely.
            # At 16×16 box size this means hotspots smaller than 6×6 px are zeroed out,
            # producing temperature reads equal to background — errors of −5°C to −100°C
            # depending on ΔT.  FLIR Thermal Studio applies no glint masking on spot meters.
            # Set "True" only when close-range images are known to contain metallic specular
