# ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║  SECTION 18 — STARTUP CONTROLLER                                        ║
# ║  Orchestrates: uvicorn thread → browser open → health monitor →        ║
# ║  Option A dialog → Tkinter fallback.                                    ║
# ║                                                                          ║
# ║  Main thread runs tkinter (required by tk on macOS/Windows).            ║
# ║  Daemon threads: uvicorn (thread 1), health monitor (thread 2).         ║
# ║  freeze_support() already called before this class is instantiated.     ║
# ║                                                                          ║
# ║  Author: Dr. Arjun Mehta / Sandra Lopez  (v3.30.22)                     ║
